§ AXIOMS  ‼ inherit PRIME_DIRECTIVE + CHARTER + §§ 30_v2 + §§ 32

  t∞: full-stack-proprietary ≡ language → compiler → substrate → engine → game
       ≡ Apocky-authored every-layer ; ¬ Unity ¬ Unreal ¬ Godot
  t∞: ¬ external-deps in-game-source
       ≡ `.csl` source ALL-game-logic ; ¬ Cargo ¬ npm @ L7
  t∞: Rust = compiler-rs HOST-side ONLY
       ≡ substrate + bridge-code + bootstrap ; ¬ game-logic-canonical
       ≡ stage-0 compiler-rs = ONLY-Rust-exception ; everything-else CSSLv3
  t∞: ∀ novel-claim audit-traceable
       ≡ ¬ "borrowed-from-X-community" ; cite-crate + cite-spec-anchor
  t∞: DoD systems-of-systems ⇒ ∀ subsystem
       cap-bound ⊕ audit-emit ⊕ replay-deterministic ⊕ stage-0-fallback
  t∞: every-feature touches ≥ 4 iterate-everywhere-axes
       ≡ input · render · audio · net · intel · procgen · audit · replay

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

§ STACK-LAYERS  «top-down · 8 layers»

  L7  GAME-LOGIC      `Labyrinth of Apockalypse/{scenes,systems}/*.csl`
                       ≡ POD-3 deliverable · `.csl` source-only
                       ≡ runtime-procgen ¬ authored-static-scenes
  L6  COMPILED-EXEC   `LoA.exe` (csslc-compiled main.cssl + linked staticlibs)
                       ≡ size 8.90 MB @ commit 1c91bc3 · LIVE-build
  L5  ENGINE-RUNTIME  `compiler-rs/crates/{loa-host,cssl-rt}`
                       ≡ MCP 110-tools · 502 lib-tests · loa-host wire-up
  L4  INTELLIGENCE    DM ⊕ GM ⊕ Collaborator ⊕ Coder narrow-orchestrators
                       ≡ cssl-host-{dm,gm,kan-real,handoff-protocol,kan-substrate-bridge}
  L3  HOST-SUPPORT    27+ cssl-host-* crates (W3..W7)
                       ≡ input · gfx · audio · net · audit · replay · handoff
  L2  SUBSTRATE       9+ cssl-substrate-* crates ⊕ ω-field-keystone
                       ≡ ω-field · KAN · audio · projections · save · prime-dir
  L1  COMPILER        `compiler-rs/crates/{csslc,cssl-rt,cssl-{spectral,fractal,render-v2}*}`
                       ≡ csslc-MIR-pipeline · cgen-{spirv,dxil,msl,wgsl,x64,cranelift}
  L0  LANGUAGE        CSLv3 spec @ `~/source/repos/CSLv3/specs/`
                       ≡ CSLv3 = notation-substrate ; CSSLv3 = compiler-impl

