§ NOVELTY-CLAIMS  «10 proprietary-edge thesis-points»

  N-1  ω-field-as-truth
       ≡ substrate-physics ¬ state-tree ¬ ECS ¬ scene-graph
       ≡ cells = first-class · Σ-mask per-cell · 7-facet 72B-aligned
       crate : cssl-substrate-omega-field          spec : §§ 30_v2

  N-2  KAN-substrate-runtime
       ≡ KAN-as-classifier-substrate ride-ON ¬ replace
       ≡ Φ-pattern-pool 10000-D HDC · KanMaterial spectral-BRDF + impedance
       crate : cssl-substrate-kan + cssl-host-kan-real    spec : 11_KAN_RIDE

  N-3  Signature-pipeline 12-stages × 6-novelty-paths multiplicative
       ≡ V.1 Wave-Unity ⊗ V.2 Spectral ⊗ V.3 Fractal-Amp ⊗
         V.4 Gaze-Collapse ⊗ V.5 HDC-Lenia ⊗ V.6 Mise-en-abyme
       ≡ EXACTLY-ONE primary-stage per-path · paths-cross via stable-API
       crate : cssl-render-v2 · cssl-spectral-render · cssl-fractal-amp ·
               cssl-gaze-collapse · cssl-hdc · cssl-wave-solver
       spec  : §§ 32

  N-4  Cap-architected-everywhere
       ≡ ∀ action sovereign-cap-bound ⊕ audit-emit
       ≡ default-deny @ caps=0 · sovereign-bypass converts deny→allow
         ALWAYS RECORDS sovereign:true (¬ silent-bypass)
       crate : cssl-caps + ∀ cssl-host-* gating-crates

  N-5  SDF-voxel-alternative
       ≡ ¬ blocky · raymarch-rendered · fractal-amplified
       ≡ smooth-organic-curves · sub-pixel-detail
       crate : cssl-render-v2 + cssl-fractal-amp

  N-6  Sovereignty-as-first-class
       ≡ player-revoke-anytime ⊕ stage-0-fallback-always
       ≡ ConsentZones spatial-regions · token-revoke single-tick propagation
       crate : cssl-substrate-prime-directive + cssl-host-attestation

  N-7  CSSL-as-game-source
       ≡ language → compiler → engine → game proprietary-stack
       ≡ L7 game-logic in-`.csl` · csslc-compiled · ¬ Rust-bootstrap
       spec  : §§ 00_THESIS · LOA_PILLARS Pillar-4

  N-8  Replay-determinism EVERYWHERE
       ≡ seed-pinned ALL · bit-equal-replay across-hosts
       ≡ Morton-key bit-spread portable (¬ BMI2-PEXT) · IEEE-754 SSE2
       crate : cssl-host-replay + cssl-substrate-omega-field

  N-9  BTreeMap-deterministic-serde
       ≡ ∀ state-store ordered-canonical ¬ HashMap-iter-noise
       ≡ JSON output bit-identical-from-seed
       pattern : cssl-host-attestation::axis_counts +
                 cssl-host-causal-seed::CausalDag::Serialize

  N-10 License::Unknown auto-rejected
       ≡ asset-bundle license-discipline · default-deny
       ≡ deny-path ¬ writes-bytes-to-disk · cache-hit STILL gate-and-register
       crate : cssl-host-asset-bundle + cssl-host-license-attribution +
               cssl-asset-fetcher

