# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

§ COMPILER-INTEGRATION  «L1 · csslc → LoA.exe»

  csslc compiles `Labyrinth of Apockalypse/main.cssl` → LoA.exe
  auto-default-link discovers `cssl-rt` + `loa-host` staticlibs
  cgen-targets : x86_64 · cranelift · spirv · dxil · msl · wgsl
  FFI-surface (cssl-rt extern-C) :
    __cssl_engine_run     | engine-tick entrypoint
    __cssl_alloc          | host-allocator hook
    __cssl_panic          | abort + audit-emit
    __cssl_audit_append   | audit-chain append
    __cssl_consent_check  | Σ-mask consult
  rule : L7 game-logic in-`.csl` · csslc-compiled · NEVER Rust-bootstrap

